# ğŸ‡²ğŸ‡º Mauritius Land Cover Change Detection System

A deep learning-based system for analyzing land cover changes in Mauritius using Sentinel-2 satellite imagery (2015-2025).

## ğŸ¯ Project Overview

This project provides:
- **Semantic segmentation** of satellite imagery into land cover classes
- **Temporal change detection** across multiple time periods
- **Interactive web interface** for visualization
- **Quantitative analysis** of land cover changes

### Land Cover Classes

| Class | Color | RGB | Description |
|-------|-------|-----|-------------|
| Roads | Grey | (128, 128, 128) | Highways, streets, paths |
| Water | Blue | (0, 100, 255) | Rivers, lakes, ocean, reservoirs |
| Forest | Dark Green | (0, 100, 0) | Natural forests, dense vegetation |
| Plantation/Crops | Light Green | (50, 205, 50) | Sugar cane, agriculture fields |
| Buildings | Brown | (139, 69, 19) | Urban areas, structures |
| Bare Land | Tan | (210, 180, 140) | Exposed soil, construction |

