1. Sefrin, O., Riese, F.M., Keller, S. (2021). Deep Learning for Land Cover Change Detection. Remote Sensing.
2. Helber, P. et al. (2019). EuroSAT: A Novel Dataset for Land Use Classification.
3. Ronneberger, O. et al. (2015). U-Net: Convolutional Networks for Biomedical Image Segmentation.

